thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by Customer Courtney/TN

author: Customer Courtney/TN
title: Customer Courtney/TN
text:
Vital Choice is the one and only place I buy seafood. I have purchased from them for years and can only give them praises.
They sell top quality seafood and their Alaskan halibut, salmon and cod fish are the cream of the crop!
In today's world quality has become a thing of the past but Vital Choice "ALWAYS" holds true to their word and you "WILL" receive Top Quality Seafood as promised.
Nothing but the highest praises for this wonderful company and their staff.
